* Iron Raptor's jaws close around Killer's torso and she then jerks her head backwards to set her teeth in place. A fair sized wound on her cheek from the shot from Killer, mech fluid leaking in abundance from it and onto the ground. With the muscles in her massive shoulders bunching she just waits there, her caught prey not going anywhere. With strain she then slams her head to the side in one giant wrence and sends her mouth into a large tree, she then wrenches her head to the other side and into a second. Bark and wood flying in all directions from the impact. She was very annoyed and once she was done with this one she would start on the second, if Prowl hadn't already taken care of him. It almost seemed to her that their attackers had no clue as to what they were getting themselves into, and it was a mistake that could mean their lives to pay with!*
